nk:type="simple"/></inline-formula>6.95、<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2580151x45_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>5820.52和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2580151x46_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>0.07分别为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2580151x47_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>、<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2580151x48_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>、<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2580151x49_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2580151x50_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的标准差。</p><p>从表2可以看出，第一主成分解释了总方差的73.875%，而前两个主成分的累计方差贡献率高达95.805%，这表明前两个主成分已经反映了原始数据95.805%的信息。由表2和表3可知，四个主成分可由标准化变量表示为：</p><table-wrap id="table2" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table2">Table 2</xref></label><caption><title> The rate of variance contribution of principal componen</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle" >主成分</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >特征根</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >方差累计贡献率(%)</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >C1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2.955</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >73.875</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >C2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.877</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >95.805</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >C3</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.167</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >99.974</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >C4</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.001</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >100</td></tr></tbody></table></table-wrap><p>表2. 主成分方差贡献率</p><table-wrap id=